sequenceDiagram
  participant Browser
  participant JobsAPI
  participant Worker

  Browser->>JobsAPI: POST /jobs
  JobsAPI->>JobsAPI: Validate payload
  JobsAPI->>Worker: Enqueue work
  Worker-->>JobsAPI: Job accepted
  JobsAPI-->>Browser: 202 Accepted + job id

  loop Poll until complete
    Browser->>JobsAPI: GET /jobs/123
    JobsAPI->>JobsAPI: Recompute aggregate status
    JobsAPI-->>Browser: queued | running | complete
  end
